    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>jumbo prawns</strong>, then add them to the spicy marinade and gently mix together until the prawns are fully coated – these are your <strong>marinated</strong> <strong>prawns</strong></p><p>Set aside for later</p>",
