      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the prawns are marinating, rinse your <strong>quinoa</strong> in a sieve under<strong> cold running water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>quinoa</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, for 6-8 min or until all the quinoa is tender</p><p>Once cooked, drain and return it to the pot until serving</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
