    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>marinated prawns</strong> and cook for 6-7 min or until the prawns are cooked through – these are your <strong>spicy jumbo king prawns</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
