      "instruction": "<p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to the cooked quinoa and give it a good mix up</p><p>Serve the <strong>spicy jumbo king prawns</strong> with the<strong> quinoa </strong>and <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>lime & coriander yoghurt</strong> all over and garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
